{"tha-ap427:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap427:0.2":"Sakimsammajjakavagga ","tha-ap427:0.3":"Korandapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap427:1.1":"“Vanakammiko pure asim, ","tha-ap427:1.2":"pitumatumatenaham; ","tha-ap427:1.3":"Pasumarena jivami, ","tha-ap427:1.4":"kusalam me na vijjati. ","tha-ap427:2.1":"Mama asayasamanta, ","tha-ap427:2.2":"tisso lokagganayako; ","tha-ap427:2.3":"Padani tini dassesi, ","tha-ap427:2.4":"anukampaya cakkhuma. ","tha-ap427:3.1":"Akkante ca pade disva, ","tha-ap427:3.2":"tissanamassa satthuno; ","tha-ap427:3.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap427:3.4":"pade cittam pasadayim. ","tha-ap427:4.1":"Korandam pupphitam disva, ","tha-ap427:4.2":"padapam dharaniruham; ","tha-ap427:4.3":"Sakosakam gahetvana, ","tha-ap427:4.4":"padasetthamapujayim. ","tha-ap427:5.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap427:5.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap427:5.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap427:5.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap427:6.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap427:6.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap427:6.3":"Korandavannakoyeva, ","tha-ap427:6.4":"suppabhaso bhavamaham. ","tha-ap427:7.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap427:7.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap427:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap427:7.4":"padapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap427:8.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap427:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap427:8.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap427:9.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap427:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap427:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap427:10.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap427:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap427:10.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap427:11.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma korandapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap427:12.1":"Korandapupphiyattherassapadanam pancamam. "}